STATE EX REL. LIVINGSTON
v.
CHERRY 2018-1432 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 22, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus and Prohibition. Relator has not filed a merit brief, due October 18, 2018, and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.
